e truth is, after Boys Don''t Cry, I realized how few and far between the great roles are. I am beyond thankful for finding Million Dollar Baby.', 14576, 0), (462640, 'I feel like I still am struggling in a lot of different ways. I still have to fight for certain things. Certain jobs. At least I''m working and I''m thankful for that.', 70321, 0), (462641, 'I''m thankful God has given us the technology where we can see each other through Skype on the computer. It''s not the same thing, but at least we can see each other. Imagine the time before when that wasn''t available and people had to go defend our country. It''s really hard. I go two weeks without seeing my family and I go crazy.', 73342, 0), (462642, 'You''re always aware that only eight per cent of actors are in work at one time, so you''ve got to be thankful for the job you''ve got and do the best you can.', 73456, 0), (462643, 'Certainly the research shows that grateful people are more innovative thinkers.', 27733, 0), (462644, 'I know for me like I have a reputation of being kind of tough, I have a reputation of also being the girl next door, kind of sweet but I have standards and my thing is, it''s me on that screen and I don''t have control over everything in this and I''m grateful and thankful.', 67182, 0), (462645, 'We have to be thankful to the Czechs that they did their duty. The Czech Republic won, I can''t believe it. It was a huge party with all the people here.', 71883, 0), (462646, 'As a husband, father and public servant, I''m thankful for the counsel and wisdom of my older brothers - Bill, who was a priest, and Kevin, who is a priest.', 72487, 0), (462647, 'I am going to spend my time today just thanking the people that played a role in my career, because I truly do believe that I was blessed by a lot of people that paths crossed mine as I went down the road in my career.', 69692, 0), (462648, 'I still don''t look at myself as a star. I''ve always had a thankful heart.', 70329, 0), (462649, 'I