d.', 70565, 0), (462691, 'I have always been thankful that so many of our country''s greatest leaders and statesmen were able to be on this earth at the same time and place to draft the Constitution.', 67490, 0), (462692, 'I''m thankful to say that I already have my dream job. I wouldn''t trade it for anything.', 73476, 0), (462693, 'As the daughter of a 25-year veteran of the armed forces, I am incredibly thankful for the sacrifices our women and men have made in Iraq, and continue to make in Afghanistan.', 73477, 0), (462694, 'I think pregnancy, like life, is what you make it. I received a good hand. I''m thankful and blessed and so peaceful and can''t wait to welcome my son.', 73478, 0), (462695, 'Working on ''Gossip Girl'' was a fantastic experience. It was my first real gig and I''m thankful for it - I got to learn a lot. I''m glad I got to explore getting comfortable in my own shoes in the background on a show like ''Gossip Girl.''', 72662, 0), (462696, 'But I''m very thankful that no one is slamming my head against the wall anymore.', 73479, 0), (462697, 'I still have a lot of the stories I wrote in high school. Hand wrote... a number of them are in purple ink, rendering them illegible, a fact we should probably be forever thankful for.', 40892, 0), (462698, 'I was pretty sheltered growing up. I just started getting into heavier music with the Tooth & Nail/Solid State era, which really kind of brought this whole thing to life for me, so I am really thankful for that label.', 73480, 0), (462699, 'I can''t say I''m thankful about being German because I sometimes experience it as a huge burden. But it is an integral part of me and I wouldn''t want to escape it. I have accepted it.', 628, 0), (462700, 'We have to be thankful considering our number as a family we enjoy very good health generally but you may be sure me and my partner have quite enough to exercise our minds and occupy our attention.', 72340, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (462701, 'Ultimately, I want to be a good person and spread happiness through my acting. If I don''t forget to be appreciative and thankful, then that would be the most important thing that I''ll ever achieve.', 73481, 0), (462702, 'I went from not knowing anything to becoming really curious and wanting to know and respecting people in the industry, realizing how hard they work. I will always be thankful for ''Top Model'' for that.', 73482, 0), (462703, 'What''s funny is my mom took me to the theater for the first time when I was six years old, and I was just amazed by it. I just said, ''Hey Mom, can I do this too?'' And so she signed me up for little theater classes, and I remember my first audition for a play when I was seven years old was for ''The Thankful Elf.''', 73483, 0), (462704, 'I''m thankful I don''t have parents that I feel I need to get their attention. They''ve always been there for me.', 73484, 0), (462705, 'I''ve done it all. I''m thankful and proud of what I''ve accomplished in my life. I hope to keep doing it.', 73485, 0), (462706, 'I''m thankful that I have lived long enough to become a legend, and I hope I deserve it.', 73485, 0), (462707, 'The act is unjustifiable that either begs for a blessing, or, having succeeded gives no thanksgiving.', 25076, 0), (462708, 'I''m just very pleased and thankful that there was a receptive audience of people that I was able to connect with.', 73486, 0), (462709, 'All the lessons you learn in film school from the people you hate are always the ones that are important. The lessons you think are great and thankful for never end up meaning anything to you.', 73487, 0), (462710, 'There are many amazing female directors that made work in more skewed times, so we should be thankful for the boundaries they pushed through.', 73488, 0), (462711, 'I feel like I''m just doing a job. It''s amazing to think that you affect other peoples'' lives on such a grand scale. I''m so thankful for that, and I''m so lucky. It''s hard to stop and think that people are interested in me.', 73489, 0), (462712, 'He enjoys much who is thankful for little.', 73490, 0), (462713, 'This little kid pointed at me and said, ''You look disgusting!'' That was the first time I thought maybe I did. I decided I''d better start eating. I''m just thankful that I made it through with relatively few scars.', 73491, 0), (462714, 'All of us, who are members of the Germanic peoples, can be happy and thankful that once in thousands of years fate has given us, from among the Germanic peoples, such a genius, a leader, our Fuehrer Adolf Hitler, and you should be happy to be allowed to work with us.', 73492, 0), (462715, 'I just find myself happy with the simple things. Appreciating the blessings God gave me.', 67702, 0), (462716, 'Friends are the siblings God never gave us.', 3003, 0), (462717, 'God gave us the gift of life it is up to us to give ourselves the gift of living well.', 808, 0), (462718, 'I''m blessed and I thank God for every day for everything that happens for me.', 2080, 0), (462719, 'Your talent is God''s gift to you. What you do with it is your gift back to God.', 406, 0), (462720, 'Do not let your hearts be troubled. Trust in God trust also in me.', 17018, 0), (462721, 'When you focus on being a blessing, God makes sure that you are always blessed in abundance.', 3956, 0), (462722, 'Talent is God given. Be humble. Fame is man-given. Be grateful. Conceit is self-given. Be careful.', 1721, 0), (462723, 'Wine is constant proof that God loves us and loves to see us happy.', 1077, 0), (462724, 'Never lose an opportunity of seeing anything beautiful, for beauty is God''s handwriting.', 760, 0), (462725, 'I believe that God put us in this jolly world to be happy and enjoy life.', 36714, 0), (462726, 'God grant me the serenity to accept the things I cannot change, the courage to change the things I can, and the wisdom to know the difference.', 1779, 0), (462727, 'I may not be where I want to be, but thank God I am not where I used to be.', 1206, 0), (462728, 'It''s just a whole different thing, and it''s just that my life has been a blessing, and I thank god every day for the gifts that he has given me and for my daughter and to be able to watch her grow and be a part of her joys and her excitement and what she wants to do in life.', 71745, 0), (462729, 'Faith is a living, daring confidence in God''s grace, so sure and certain that a man could stake his life on it a thousand times.', 1746, 0), (462730, 'God writes the Gospel not in the Bible alone, but also on trees, and in the flowers and clouds and stars.', 1746, 0), (462731, 'I just thank God for all of the blessings.', 22838, 0), (462732, 'If we ever forget that we are One Nation Under God, then we will be a nation gone under.', 1727, 0), (462733, 'The thing to do, it seems to me, is to prepare yourself so you can be a rainbow in somebody else''s cloud. Somebody who may not look like you. May not call God the same name you call God - if they call God at all. I may not dance your dances or speak your language. But be a blessing to somebody. That''s what I think.', 74, 0), (462734, 'The most important lesson that I have learned is to trust God in every circumstance. Lots of times we go through different trials and following God''s plan seems like it doesn''t make any sense at all. God is always in control and he will never leave us.', 32778, 0), (462735, 'God never ends anything on a negative God always ends on a positive.', 12361, 0), (462736, 'Woman is a ray of God. She is not that earthly beloved: she is creative, not created.', 20453, 0), (462737, 'Whosoever is delighted in solitude is either a wild beast or a god.', 1116, 0), (462738, 'It''s a struggle for every young Black man. You know how it is, only God can judge us.', 1097, 0), (462739, 'I cannot and will not recant anything, for to go against conscience is neither right nor safe. Here I stand, I can do no other, so help me God. Amen.', 1746, 0), (462740, 'It doesn''t matter where you come from, what you have or don''t have, what you lack, or what you have too much of. But all you need to have is faith in God, an undying passion for what you do and what you choose to do in this life, and a relentless drive and the will to do whatever it takes to be successful in whatever you put your mind to.', 69121, 0), (462741, 'God has given you one face, and you make yourself another.', 13, 0), (462742, 'I believe that God has put gifts and talents and ability on the inside of every one of us. When you develop that and you believe in yourself and you believe that you''re a person of influence and a person of purpose, I believe you can rise up out of any situation.', 3956, 0), (462743, 'If you''re white and you''re wrong, then you''re wrong; if you''re black and you''re wrong, you''re wrong. People are people. Black, blue, pink, green - God make no rules about color; only society make rules where my people suffer, and that why we must have redemption and redemption now.', 7, 0), (462744, 'I will thank God for the day and the moment I have.', 756, 0), (462745, 'God used beautiful mathematics in creating the world.', 70906, 0), (462746, 'God already knows what we''re made of, but perhaps He wants us to learn what we''re made of. I think we would all agree that we learn more from our tough times than from our easy times.', 881, 0), (462747, 'Where can we go to find God if we cannot see Him in our own hearts and in every living being.', 1838, 0), (462748, 'God has given us two hands, one to receive with and the other to give with.', 4008, 0), (462749, 'One of the greatest attacks of the enemy is to make you busy, to make you hurried, to make you noisy, to make you distracted, to fill the people of God and the Church of God with so much noise and activity that there is no room for prayer. There is no room for being alone with God. There is no room for silence. There is no room for meditation.', 69572, 0), (462750, 'It is foolish and wrong to mourn the men who died. Rather we should thank God that such men lived.', 57896, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (462751, 'God gave you a gift of 86,400 seconds today. Have you used one to say ''thank you?''', 1820, 0), (462752, 'Stupidity is also a gift of God, but one mustn''t misuse it.', 66871, 0), (462753, 'Ignorance is the curse of God knowledge is the wing wherewith we fly to heaven.', 13, 0), (462754, 'I have held many things in my hands, and I have lost them all; but whatever I have placed in God''s hands, that I still possess.', 1746, 0), (462755, 'A baby is God''s opinion that life should go on.', 1301, 0), (462756, 'In the first place, God made idiots. That was for practice. Then he made school boards.', 286, 0), (462757, 'The most important thing is God''s blessing and if you believe in God and you believe in yourself, you have nothing to worry about.', 73493, 0), (462758, 'Beautiful music is the art of the prophets that can calm the agitations of the soul it is one of the most magnificent and delightful presents God has given us.', 1746, 0), (462759, 'Oh, these vast, calm, measureless mountain days, days in whose light everything seems equally divine, opening a thousand windows to show us God.', 1402, 0), (462760, 'Anyone can count the seeds in an apple, but only God can count the number of apples in a seed.', 1935, 0), (462761, 'I have had a happy life and thank the Lord. Goodbye and may God bless all!', 1344, 0), (462762, 'Keep your nose out the sky, keep your heart to god, and keep your face to the raising sun.', 3290, 0), (462763, 'A dog barks when his master is attacked. I would be a coward if I saw that God''s truth is attacked and yet would remain silent.', 4271, 0), (462764, 'There''s a tremendous difference between alone and lonely. You could be lonely in a group of people. I like being alone. I like eating by myself. I go home at night and just watch a movie or hang out with my dog. I have to exert myself and really say, oh God, I''ve got to see my friends ''cause I''m too content being by myself.', 292, 0), (462765, 'I can make a lord, but only God can make a gentleman.', 73494, 0), (462766, 'I believe in Jesus Christ as my Lord and savior. I believe that Jesus died for my sins, and rose again, and that''s my belief. I still don''t know what ''Christian'' means. I''m a follower of Christ, but I keep making a whole bunch of mistakes. And I thank God for forgiveness.', 73210, 0), (462767, 'In the absence of any other proof, the thumb alone would convince me of God''s existence.', 2482, 0), (462768, 'God made you a masterpiece - be blessed, secure, disciplined and equipped.', 3956, 0), (462769, 'Don''t you know there ain''t no devil, it''s just god when he''s drunk.', 2201, 0), (462770, 'Our heavenly Father understands our disappointment, suffering, pain, fear, and doubt. He is always there to encourage our hearts and help us understand that He''s sufficient for all of our needs. When I accepted this as an absolute truth in my life, I found that my worrying stopped.', 67762, 0), (462771, 'Disappointment is inevitable. But to become discouraged, there''s a choice I make. God would never discourage me. He would always point me to himself to trust him. Therefore, my discouragement is from Satan. As you go through the emotions that we have, hostility is not from God, bitterness, unforgiveness, all of these are attacks from Satan.', 67762, 0), (462772, 'I am a person who always tries not to be easily influenced by position or achievement. I thank God for the fact that I can share more kindness and a good quality of life through the popularity. Not for the popularity itself.', 68843, 0), (462773, 'The word ''Islam'' means ''peace.'' The word ''Muslim'' means ''one who surrenders to God.'' But the press makes us seem like haters.', 1751, 0), (462774, 'Our Lord has written the promise of resurrection, not in books alone, but in every leaf in springtime.', 1746, 0), (462775, 'As a child of God, I am greater than anything that can happen to me.', 1798, 0), (462776, 'Perhaps nothing helps us make the movement from our little selves to a larger world than remembering God in gratitude. Such a perspective puts God in view in all of life, not just in the moments we set aside for worship or spiritual disciplines. Not just in the moments when life seems easy.', 19097, 0), (462777, 'If you expect the blessings of God, be kind to His people.', 70609, 0), (462778, 'Judge me if you want to. And as a matter of fact, it won''t even count, ''cause the only person who can judge is God.', 67572, 0), (462779, 'People face difficulties, no matter who you are. I faced difficulties with a lot of things. I face opposition every day, but I didn''t kill myself and now, thank God, I''m here.', 2069, 0), (462780, 'Non-violence requires a double faith, faith in God and also faith in man.', 32, 0), (462781, 'A person once asked me, in a provocative manner, if I approved of homosexuality. I replied with another question: ''Tell me: when God looks at a gay person, does he endorse the existence of this person with love, or reject and condemn this person?'' We must always consider the person.', 6248, 0), (462782, 'Honesty is of God and dishonesty of the devil the devil was a liar from the beginning.', 4294, 0), (462783, 'A man can no more diminish God''s glory by refusing to worship Him than a lunatic can put out the sun by scribbling the word, ''darkness'' on the walls of his cell.', 26, 0), (462784, 'The Christian life is not a constant high. I have my moments of deep discouragement. I have to go to God in prayer with tears in my eyes, and say, ''O God, forgive me,'' or ''Help me.''', 4008, 0), (462785, 'He who learns must suffer. And even in our sleep pain that cannot forget falls drop by drop upon the heart, and in our own despair, against our will, comes wisdom to us by the awful grace of God.', 1882, 0), (462786, 'Beauty is mysterious as well as terrible. God and devil are fighting there, and the battlefield is the heart of man.', 67334, 0), (462787, 'Whatever your heart clings to and confides in, that is really your God.', 1746, 0), (462788, 'I tremble for my country when I reflect that God is just that his justice cannot sleep forever.', 1207, 0), (462789, 'Bottom line: God will not allow any person to keep you from your destiny. They may be bigger, stronger, or more powerful, but God knows how to shift things around and get you to where you''re supposed to be.', 3956, 0), (462790, 'We Marines believe that God gave America the greatest gift He could bestow to man while he lived on this earth -freedom. We also believe He gave us another gift nearly as precious - our soldiers, sailors, airmen, Coast Guardsmen, and Marines - to safeguard that gift and guarantee no force on this earth can ever steal it away.', 73495, 0), (462791, 'Sir, my concern is not whether God is on our side; my greatest concern is to be on God''s side, for God is always right.', 1012, 0), (462792, 'I know that there''s a god because I was able to survive everything that I''ve been through - all of the tough times - and I''m still at the top of my game.', 67644, 0), (462793, 'If I could give you information of my life, it would be to show how a woman of very ordinary ability has been led by God in strange and unaccustomed paths to do In His service what He has done in her. And if I could tell you all, you would see how God has done all, and I nothing.', 4085, 0), (462794, 'The moment I have realized God sitting in the temple of every human body, the moment I stand in reverence before every human being and see God in him - that moment I am free from bondage, everything that binds vanishes, and I am free.', 1838, 0), (462795, 'I die the king''s faithful servant, but God''s first.', 2628, 0), (462796, 'I believe that life is a journey towards God, and that no one has the right to insist that you go a certain road.', 69892, 0), (462797, 'When the solution is simple, God is answering.', 104, 0), (462798, 'My father always taught me that when you help other people, then God will give you double. And that''s what has really happened to me. When I have helped other people who are in need, God has helped me more.', 5874, 0), (462799, 'I would rather die than do something which I know to be a sin, or to be against God''s will.', 63110, 0), (462800, 'For where God built a church, there the Devil would also build a chapel.', 1746, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (462801, 'No man is excluded from calling upon God, the gate of salvation is set open unto all men: neither is there any other thing which keepeth us back from entering in, save only our own unbelief.', 4271, 0), (462802, 'In my country of South Africa, we struggled for years against the evil system of apartheid that divided human beings, children of the same God, by racial classification and then denied many of them fundamental human rights.', 2109, 0), (462803, 'To my young friends out there: Life can be great, but not when you can''t see it. So, open your eyes to life: to see it in the vivid colors that God gave us as a precious gift to His children, to enjoy life to the fullest, and to make it count. Say yes to your life.', 7879, 0), (462804, 'Socialism has no moral justification whatsoever; poor people are not morally superior to rich people, nor are they owed anything by rich people simply because of their lack of success. Charity is not a socialist concept - it is a religious one, an acknowledgment of God''s sovereignty over property, a sovereignty the Left utterly rejects.', 17797, 0), (462805, 'We were born to die and we die to live. As seedlings of God, we barely blossom on earth; we fully flower in heaven.', 71238, 0), (462806, 'The Bible is one of the greatest blessings bestowed by God on the children of men. It has God for its author; salvation for its end, and truth without any mixture for its matter. It is all pure.', 2375, 0), (462807, 'Forgiveness is God''s command.', 1746, 0), (462808, 'Until we meet again, may God bless you as he has blessed me.', 1120, 0), (462809, 'God removes the sin of the one who makes humble confession, and thereby the devil loses the sovereignty he had gained over the human heart.', 65719, 0), (462810, 'There is but One God. His name is Truth He is the Creator. He fears none he is without hate. He never dies He is beyond the cycle of births and death. He is self-illuminated. He is realized by the kindness of the True Guru. He was True in the beginning He was True when the ages commenced and has ever been True. He is also True now.', 4201, 0), (462811, 'God made the Idiot for practice, and then He made the School Board.', 286, 0), (462812, 'When you find your definitions in God, you find the very purpose for which you were created. Put your hand into God''s hand, know His absolutes, demonstrate His love, present His truth, and the message of redemption and transformation will take hold.', 4001, 0), (462813, 'It''s up to God to do the judging. You haven''t walked in my boots, so how are you going to judge me?', 67027, 0), (462814, 'Socialism violates at least three of the Ten Commandments: It turns government into God, it legalizes thievery and it elevates covetousness. Discussions of income inequality, after all, aren''t about prosperity but about petty spite. Why should you care how much money I make, so long as you are happy?', 17797, 0), (462815, 'Allowing myself to love God completely has obviously shed light on my self-love because he loves me more than I could ever love myself.', 52738, 0), (462816, 'There are two kinds of people: those who say to God, ''Thy will be done,'' and those to whom God says, ''All right, then, have it your way.''', 26, 0), (462817, 'Those who deny freedom to others deserve it not for themselves; and under the rule of a just God, cannot long retain it.', 1012, 0), (462818, 'God is bigger than people think.', 23263, 0), (462819, 'My job is to perform, enjoy cricket and thank God for whatever he has given me.', 67900, 0), (462820, 'God works wonders now and then; Behold a lawyer, an honest man.', 1077, 0), (462821, 'Zen does not confuse spirituality with thinking about God while one is peeling potatoes. Zen spirituality is just to peel the potatoes.', 45466, 0), (462822, 'If I am not, may God put me there; and if I am, may God so keep me.', 63110, 0), (462823, 'We cannot embrace God''s forgiveness if we are so busy clinging to past wounds and nursing old grudges.', 225, 0), (462824, 'Kill a man, and you are an assassin. Kill millions of men, and you are a conqueror. Kill everyone, and you are a god.', 73496, 0), (462825, 'I think that the greatest gift God ever gave man is not the gift of sight but the gift of vision. Sight is a function of the eyes, but vision is a function of the heart.', 11162, 0), (462826, 'God is all-full. He is self-contained. He is eternal satisfaction.', 62960, 0), (462827, 'I most certainly believe that it is the gift of God that I am what I am. And so I dwell amongst barbarians, a proselyte and an exile, for the love of God.', 66870, 0), (462828, 'A dark cloud is no sign that the sun has lost his light and dark black convictions are no arguments that God has laid aside His mercy.', 36532, 0), (462829, 'I would love it if people could look at chubby folks with all of our curves, bumps and ridges and just say ''She''s beautiful'' just like that. You don''t have to get on a treadmill as long as your blood pressure is under control and you eat healthy, God bless.', 73497, 0), (462830, 'God is the indwelling and not the transient cause of all things.', 2478, 0), (462831, 'It is not fitting, when one is in God''s service, to have a gloomy face or a chilling look.', 1681, 0), (462832, 'I try to give to the poor people for love what the rich could get for money. No, I wouldn''t touch a leper for a thousand pounds; yet I willingly cure him for the love of God.', 70, 0), (462833, 'Rebellion against tyrants is obedience to God.', 1077, 0), (462834, 'Prayer doesn''t just change things - it changes us. If we are diligent in seeking God, slowly and surely we become better people.', 1206, 0), (462835, 'If you are caught on a golf course during a storm and are afraid of lightning, hold up a 1-iron. Not even God can hit a 1-iron.', 62911, 0), (462836, 'Being out there in the ocean, God''s creation, it''s like a gift He has given us to enjoy.', 10127, 0), (462837, 'Salvation brings the soul a deep awareness of God''s love. Life takes on more meaning, for it now has a purpose.', 9130, 0), (462838, 'Man gives you the award but God gives you the reward.', 5253, 0), (462839, 'We live in a culture that relishes tearing others down. It''s ultimately more fulfilling, though, to help people reach their goals. Instead of feeling jealous, remember: If God did it for them, He can do it for you.', 3956, 0), (462840, 'God, give us grace to accept with serenity the things that cannot be changed, courage to change the things which should be changed and the wisdom to distinguish the one from the other.', 1779, 0), (462841, 'You shall love the Lord your God with all your heart and with all your soul and with all your might. And these words that I command you today shall be on your heart. You shall teach them diligently to your children, and shall talk of them when you sit in your house, and when you walk by the way, and when you lie down, and when you rise.', 71378, 0), (462842, 'Behold, I stand at the door and knock. If anyone hears my voice and opens the door, I will come in to him and eat with him, and he with me.', 17018, 0), (462843, 'Everything I did, all my actions, all of the problems I had I dedicate to God and to Chile, because I kept Chile from becoming Communist.', 73498, 0), (462844, 'You learn from the things that happen in your career. You get up and down. You never give up. All the things that happened in my career, thank God it happened early rather than late in my career.', 72057, 0), (462845, 'Let us more and more insist on raising funds of love, of kindness, of understanding, of peace. Money will come if we seek first the Kingdom of God - the rest will be given.', 70, 0), (462846, 'God can cause opportunity to find you. He has unexpected blessings where you suddenly meet the right person, or suddenly your health improves, or suddenly you''re able to pay off your house. That''s God shifting things in your favor.', 3956, 0), (462847, 'God put us here to prepare this place for the next generation. That''s our job. Raising children and helping the community, that''s preparing for the next generation.', 71155, 0), (462848, 'I don''t know. Only God knows where the story ends for me, but I know where the story begins. It''s up to us to choose, whether we win or lose and I choose to win.', 47442, 0), (462849, 'The message is that I was reminding myself and informing others of the fact that God has always been good to me. No matter what you''re going through, God is always with us. Life is a journey.', 73499, 0), (462850, 'Good man! Genuine gentleman! God bless George Thompson, the great-hearted friend of my race.', 2013, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (462851, 'Me don''t dip on nobody''s side. Me don''t dip on the black man''s side, not the white man''s side. Me dip on God''s side, the one who create me and cause me to come from black and white.', 7, 0), (462852, 'We are all gifted, but we have to discover the gift, uncover the gift, nurture and develop the gift and use it for the Glory of God and for the liberation struggle of our people.', 51994, 0), (462853, 'I am inclined to believe that this is the land God gave to Cain.', 73500, 0), (462854, 'The eye with which I see God is the same eye with which God sees me.', 418, 0), (462855, 'Charity is a supreme virtue, and the great channel through which the mercy of God is passed onto mankind.', 11167, 0), (462856, 'May God save the country, for it is evident that the people will not.', 58652, 0), (462857, 'God can be realized through all paths. All religions are true. The important thing is to reach the roof. You can reach it by stone stairs or by wooden stairs or by bamboo steps or by a rope. You can also climb up by a bamboo pole.', 4269, 0), (462858, 'From my point of view, God is the light that illuminates the darkness, even if it does not dissolve it, and a spark of divine light is within each of us.', 6248, 0), (462859, 'Find new ways to spread the word of God to every corner of the world.', 6248, 0), (462860, 'As a surgeon you have to have a controlled arrogance. If it''s uncontrolled, you kill people, but you have to be pretty arrogant to saw through a person''s chest, take out their heart and believe you can fix it. Then, when you succeed and the patient survives, you pray, because it''s only by the grace of God that you get there.', 72135, 0), (462861, 'Faith is about trusting God when you have unanswered questions.', 3956, 0), (462862, 'As God has not made anything useless in this world, as all beings fulfill obligations or a role in the sublime drama of Creation, I cannot exempt from this duty, and small though it be, I too have a mission to fill, as for example: alleviating the sufferings of my fellowmen.', 3961, 0), (462863, 'When God sneezed, I didn''t know what to say.', 11800, 0), (462864, 'The straight line belongs to men, the curved one to God.', 21412, 0), (462865, 'Find out how much God has given you and from it take what you need the remainder is needed by others.', 63060, 0), (462866, 'Being a singer is a natural gift. It means I''m using to the highest degree possible the gift that God gave me to use. I''m happy with that.', 67725, 0), (462867, 'Every day, I get closer to God. Every day, my will to do the right thing gets stronger.', 67702, 0), (462868, 'If God listened to the prayers of men, all men would quickly have perished: for they are forever praying for evil against one another.', 1839, 0), (462869, 'Since God had commanded it, it was necessary that I do it. Since God commanded it, even if I had a hundred fathers and mothers, even if I had been a King''s daughter, I would have gone nevertheless.', 63110, 0), (462870, 'Material possessions, winning scores, and great reputations are meaningless in the eyes of the Lord, because He knows what we really are and that is all that matters.', 1721, 0), (462871, 'God doesn''t dwell in the wooden, stony or earthen idols. His abode is in our feelings, our thoughts.', 25555, 0), (462872, 'The voice of the people has been said to be the voice of God; and, however generally this maxim has been quoted and believed, it is not true to fact. The people are turbulent and changing, they seldom judge or determine right.', 16733, 0), (462873, 'What God intended for you goes far beyond anything you can imagine.', 588, 0), (462874, 'God may be in the details, but the goddess is in the questions. Once we begin to ask them, there''s no turning back.', 1739, 0), (462875, 'An angel of God never has wings.', 3554, 0), (462876, 'Give me one hundred preachers who fear nothing but sin and desire nothing but God, and I c