ss.', 16749, 0), (463265, 'You seek the heights of manhood when you seek the depths of God.', 12361, 0), (463266, 'Live, so you do not have to look back and say: ''God, how I have wasted my life.''', 1080, 0), (463267, 'I know it''s an experience that I need to have if God''s putting me through it.', 2080, 0), (463268, 'I was very, very religious. And of course I wrote about it in ''Night.'' I questioned God''s silence. So I questioned. I don''t have an answer for that. Does it mean that I stopped having faith? No. I have faith, but I question it.', 10, 0), (463269, 'God is not upset that Gandhi was not a Christian, because God is not a Christian! All of God''s children and their different faiths help us to realize the immensity of God.', 2109, 0), (463270, 'God''s the final judge for Elvis Presley and Johnny Cash too. That''s solely in the hands of God.', 3959, 0), (463271, 'If God did not exist, it would be necessary to invent Him.', 808, 0), (463272, 'Since His delights are to be with you, let yours be found in Him.', 67483, 0), (463273, 'Most laws condemn the soul and pronounce sentence. The result of the law of my God is perfect. It condemns but forgives. It restores - more than abundantly - what it takes away.', 1892, 0), (463274, 'Me, I''m spiritually retarded, I need to be knee deep in water with a fly rod in my hands, that''s about as close to God as I get.', 55413, 0), (463275, 'The finite is annihilated in the presence of the infinite, and becomes a pure nothing. So our spirit before God, so our justice before divine justice.', 144, 0), (463276, 'He was a wise man who originated the idea of God.', 542, 0), (463277, 'They always win who side with God.', 27036, 0), (463278, 'Some of God''s greatest gifts are unanswered prayers.', 56259, 0), (463279, 'Nothing that is God''s is obtainable by money.', 3445, 0), (463280, 'Sometimes you ask God for something and you don''t know what you''re asking.', 18404, 0), (463281, 'Sometimes God writes straightforward in twisted lines.', 73517, 0), (463282, 'My message is that God is a good God.', 3956, 0), (463283, 'If you must be mad, be it not for the things of the world. Be mad with the love of God.', 4269, 0), (463284, 'Your God is ever beside you - indeed, He is even within you.', 67483, 0), (463285, 'The world sees in our conduct, in our behaviour, the proof that we are the real children of God.', 72780, 0), (463286, 'When God hands you a gift, he also hands you a whip; and the whip is intended for self-flagellation solely.', 262, 0), (463287, 'The first revolt is against the supreme tyranny of theology, of the phantom of God. As long as we have a master in heaven, we will be slaves on earth.', 3973, 0), (463288, 'Where love is, there God is also.', 32, 0), (463289, 'The romantic love we feel toward the opposite sex is probably one extra help from God to bring you together, but that''s it. All the rest of it, the true love, is the test.', 71569, 0), (463290, 'God is everywhere but He is most manifest in man. So serve man as God. That is as good as worshipping God.', 4269, 0), (463291, 'Among the children of God, it was they who were most able to rightly divide the word of truth.', 73518, 0), (463292, 'The point is that knowledge of God is not prohibited under the First Amendment.', 66757, 0), (463293, 'God made the integers all else is the work of man.', 73519, 0), (463294, 'I want to love all the children of God - Christian, Jew, Moslem, Hindu, Buddhist - everyone. I want to love gay Christians and straight Christians.', 618, 0), (463295, 'The hardest people to reach with the love of God are not the bad people. They know they are bad. They have no defense. The hardest ones to win for God are the self-righteous people.', 64371, 0), (463296, 'God comes first - if I don''t love him, I can''t love anybody, and if I can''t love me I can''t love nobody.', 47442, 0), (463297, 'And I asked my mother about it; I said, ''Is there something wrong?'' She said, ''God... God makes people. 